                <h3>HR Rounds</h3>
                <p>Practice behavioral questions and learn how to showcase your soft skills and experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-network-wired"></i>
                <h3>System Design</h3>
                <p>Tackle system design problems and learn how to architect scalable and efficient solutions.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section_title">Mock Tests</h2>
        <div class="grid-container">
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-calculator"></i>
                <h3>Aptitude Tests</h3>
                <p>Sharpen your quantitative skills with practice questions and time-management strategies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i>
                <h3>Logical & Reasoning</h3>
                <p>Develop your critical thinking abilities with logical puzzles and reasoning questions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-terminal"></i>
