                <p>Improve your coding skills in various languages with challenging programming problems.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section_title">Resume Builder</h2>
        <div class="grid-container">
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-file"></i>
                <h3>Create Resume</h3>
                <p>Use our intuitive builder to create a professional and effective resume.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i>
                <h3>Download Resume</h3>
                <p>Download your resume in various formats and share it with potential employers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-edit"></i>
                <h3>Edit Resume</h3>
                <p>Make changes and keep your resume updated to reflect your latest skills and experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                <h3>ATS Score & Analysis</h3>
                <p>Optimize your resume for Applicant Tracking Systems and increase your chances of getting noticed.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>